::Reptilica::

Reptilica recieves the message, sending a reply and tapping a few 
buttons to send orders to the shuttle. The reply read: "Ok. I'll have 
the shuttle get back to base. We'll be able to fix her up here if she 
wants."

He turns to the new recruits. "Allright, enough waiting for 
Wheeljack. Lets see how the building is going."

He motions for them to follow, walking over to where Wheeljack 
is. "Progress report?" he asks as he approaches him.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
The shuttle's engines power up, lifting a bit off the ground. It 
would wait untill all the bots were in and then it would close the 
hatch and return to the Iron Fist.
